# Getting Started

## Start

```bash
./scripts/start.sh
```

Default port is 8010. Open: http://localhost:8010/

## Use an external config.yaml

```bash
CONFIG=/path/to/config.yaml ./scripts/start.sh
```

Or:

```bash
.venv/bin/python -m backend.serve --config /path/to/config.yaml --port 8010
```

## LLM configuration

1) Copy config
- config.example.yaml -> config.yaml

2) Key fields
- llm.enabled: true
- llm.base_url: OpenAI-compatible API URL
- llm.api_key: API key
- llm.model: model name

## Usage

1) Upload .docx (/api/upload)
2) Run:
- Decompose (/api/decompose)
- Schedule (/api/schedule)
- Estimate (/api/estimate)
3) Download artifacts
